elements.name: censusWarningConditionCode
elements.description:
The anticipated ACE generated code that identifies the Census warning condition.

  • *CENSUS* IMPROBABLE COUNTRY.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 01, 02, 03, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* MAXIMUM VALUE EXCEEDED.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 51

  • *CENSUS* QTY1/QTY2.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 09, 20, 21, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* QTY2/QTY1.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 09, 20, 21, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* OR-HI VAL/QTY (1).

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 04, 05, 06, 07, 08, 09, 10, 11, 15, 21, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* OR-HI VAL/QTY (2).

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 04, 05, 06, 07, 08, 09, 10, 11, 15, 21, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* OR-LO VAL/QTY (1).

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 09, 12, 13, 14, 15, 20, 27, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* OR-LO VAL/QTY (2).

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 09, 12, 13, 14, 15, 20, 27, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* IMPROBABLE AIR TARIFF.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 05, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* GROSS WEIGHT - VESSEL.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 20, 22, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* GROSS WEIGHT - AIR.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 20, 22, 49, 50

  • *CENSUS* MAXIMUM CHARGES EXCEEDED.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 51

  • *CENSUS* OR-AGR CHARGES/VALUE.

    Acceptable Census Condition Override Code(s): 05, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20, 22, 49, 50

elements.name: censusWarningConditionOverrideCode
elements.description: A code that identifies the reason that the submitted data values caused the Census warning condition; the override code.

options.20: Weight of Article Heavier Than Normal
options.21: Weight of Article Lighter Than Normal
options.24: Non-product Line Item Needed to Conduct Business
options.25: Beginning to Import New Product Line
